@node Main "Zarro - Documentation"

                          'Zarro' 1.0

                        by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Zarro' is a @{" Workbench game " link play} where you have to move any of the
four (4) arrows in order to create series of 4 or more tiles of
the same type, these series of tiles must be either horizontal or
vertical. As a series of tiles of the same type is made, they
disappear and you get points according to the number of tiles.

  Avoid leaving less than 4 tiles of a type on the board, as that
would eventually end the game...

  Have fun!

